		<h2>MMA Actors, Transactions, and Content Modules</h2>
		<p>This section defines the actors, transactions, and content modules in this profile. General definitions of actors are given in the Technical Frameworks General Introduction Appendix A at <a href="http://ihe.net/Technical_Frameworks/#GenIntro">http://ihe.net/Technical_Frameworks/#GenIntro</a>.</p>
		<p>Figure X.1-1 shows the actors directly involved in the MMA Profile and the relevant transactions between them.</p>
		<p>The MMA Profile consists of two reusable purpose transactions and actor sets:</p>
		<ol>
			<li>The interaction for getting medication administration requests</li>
			<li>The interaction for reporting medication administrations</li>
		</ol>
		<p>Figure X.1-1: MMA Actor Diagram</p>
